Here’s a self-contained HTML + CSS example that implements everything you asked for. You can drop this into a file (e.g. `index.html`), replace the placeholder logo/src and hero image URL, and tweak colors or fonts as needed.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Corporate Page</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset some defaults */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #000;
    }

    /* Sticky header */
    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: #fff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 1rem;
      height: 60px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      z-index: 1000;
    }
    .logo img {
      height: 40px;
    }

    /* Navigation */
    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    nav li {
      position: relative;
    }
    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #000;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    /* Arrow indicator for items with submenu */
    nav li.has-submenu > a::after {
      content: '▼';
      font-size: 0.6em;
      margin-left: 0.25em;
    }
    /* Submenu */
    nav ul.submenu {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      top: 100%;
      left: 0;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      min-width: 150px;
    }
    nav ul.submenu li {
      width: 100%;
    }
    nav li.has-submenu:hover > ul.submenu {
      display: block;
    }

    /* Hero section */
    .hero {
      height: 400px;
      background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1200x400') center/cover no-repeat;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .hero .cta {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* Content sections */
    .content {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }
    .light {
      background: #f7f7f7;
    }
    .dark {
      background: #eaeaea;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background: #333;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    footer p {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    footer a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <!-- Replace with your actual logo -->
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150x40?text=Logo" alt="Corporate Logo">
    </div>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
        <li class="has-submenu">
          <a href="#">About Us</a>
          <ul class="submenu">
            <li><a href="#">Our Mission</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Team</a></li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li class="has-submenu">
          <a href="#">Services</a>
          <ul class="submenu">
            <li><a href="#">Consulting</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Implementation</a></li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li><a href="#">Products</a></li>
        <li class="has-submenu">
          <a href="#">Resources</a>
          <ul class="submenu">
            <li><a href="#">Blog</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Webinars</a></li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <a href="#signup" class="cta">Get Started Today</a>
  </section>

  <section class="content light">
    <h2>Section 1</h2>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer nec odio.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content dark">
    <h2>Section 2</h2>
    <p>Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam. Sed nisi.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content light">
    <h2>Section 3</h2>
    <p>Nulla quis sem at nibh elementum imperdiet. Duis sagittis ipsum.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content dark">
    <h2>Section 4</h2>
    <p>Praesent mauris. Fusce nec tellus sed augue semper porta.</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Your Company Name</p>
    <p>123 Business Rd, Suite 456, City, Country</p>
    <p><a href="mailto:info@yourcompany.com">info@yourcompany.com</a> | +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
```

**How it works**  
- **Header** is `position: sticky; top: 0` so it stays fixed on scroll.  
- **Logo** on the left, **navigation** on the right using a flex container.  
- Menu items with submenus have the class `.has-submenu`; CSS adds a ▼ arrow via `::after`, and shows the dropdown on `:hover`.  
- **Hero** uses a full-width background image and centers a call-to-action link.  
- **Content sections** alternate between `.light` and `.dark` backgrounds (#f7f7f7 vs. #eaeaea) that are light enough for black text.  
- **Footer** has your corporate info.

Feel free to adjust spacing, colors, fonts, images, and breakpoints to match your brand.
